'ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-hoi-nghi-khach-hang-doi-tac-chuyen-nghiep-tai-mien-bac.html\/#Hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac_la_gi\" title=\"H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0\">H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-hoi-nghi-khach-hang-doi-tac-chuyen-nghiep-tai-mien-bac.html\/#Vi_sao_doanh_nghiep_nen_to_chuc_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac\" title=\"V\u00ec sao doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u00ean t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c?\">V\u00ec sao doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u00ean t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-hoi-nghi-khach-hang-doi-tac-chuyen-nghiep-tai-mien-bac.html\/#Quy_trinh_to_chuc_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac_cua_A_Chau_Media\" title=\"Quy tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media\u00a0\">Quy tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media\u00a0<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3'><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-hoi-nghi-khach-hang-doi-tac-chuyen-nghiep-tai-mien-bac.html\/#Len_danh_sach_khach_moi\" title=\"L\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi\">L\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-hoi-nghi-khach-hang-doi-tac-chuyen-nghiep-tai-mien-bac.html\/#Len_y_tuong\" title=\"L\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng\">L\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-hoi-nghi-khach-hang-doi-tac-chuyen-nghiep-tai-mien-bac.html\/#Xay_dung_ke_hoach_ho_so\" title=\"X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ed3 s\u01a1\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ed3 s\u01a1<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-hoi-nghi-khach-hang-doi-tac-chuyen-nghiep-tai-mien-bac.html\/#Trien_khai_ke_hoach\" title=\"Tri\u1ec3n khai k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch\">Tri\u1ec3n khai k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-hoi-nghi-khach-hang-doi-tac-chuyen-nghiep-tai-mien-bac.html\/#To_chuc_chuong_trinh_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac\" title=\"T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c\">T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/dich-vu-to-chuc-hoi-nghi-khach-hang-doi-tac-chuyen-nghiep-tai-mien-bac.html\/#Ket_thuc_chuong_trinh_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac\" title=\"K\u1ebft th\u00fac ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><em><strong>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u media<\/strong> t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ty t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam; c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c\u00a0v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u quy m\u00f4 v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1ch nhau. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m, vi\u1ec7c kh\u1ea3o s\u00e1t \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, \u00fd ngh\u0129a, th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p v\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a\u00a0<strong>h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn, gi\u00fap cho qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n\u00a0<strong>t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/strong>\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c di\u1ec5n ra nhanh ch\u00f3ng, thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng t\u1ed1i \u01b0u y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p, t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb v\u00e0 l\u1ee3i \u00edch c\u1ee7a<strong>\u00a0h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac_la_gi\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c l\u00e0 g\u00ec?\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>H\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c<\/strong>\u00a0l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ed1i tho\u1ea1i, li\u00ean k\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c th\u0103m d\u00f2 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 duy tr\u00ec m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u0169 v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat th\u00eam kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng trung th\u00e0nh, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<p>Trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5\u00a0<strong>h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c<\/strong>, doanh nghi\u1ec7p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ed3ng gh\u00e9p gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m m\u1edbi ho\u1eb7c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch \u01b0u \u0111\u00e3i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14393 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"480\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Vi_sao_doanh_nghiep_nen_to_chuc_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>V\u00ec sao doanh nghi\u1ec7p n\u00ean t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c?<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Th\u00f4ng qua g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1, giao l\u01b0u v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft, doanh nghi\u1ec7p s\u1ebd gia t\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p, b\u00e0y t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam nh\u1eefng kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14388 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1692\" height=\"1128\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Quy_trinh_to_chuc_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac_cua_A_Chau_Media\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>Quy tr\u00ecnh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c c\u1ee7a \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media\u00a0<\/strong><\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14389 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1100\" height=\"716\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Len_danh_sach_khach_moi\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">L\u00ean danh s\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Danh s\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng trong\u00a0<strong>h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c,<\/strong>\u00a0<strong>doanh nghi\u1ec7p<\/strong> c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi, \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m, d\u1ef1 tr\u00f9 kinh ph\u00ed c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi. \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi danh s\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch m\u1eddi v\u00e0 chi ph\u00ed c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Len_y_tuong\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">L\u00ean \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd g\u1ee3i \u00fd nh\u1eefng \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o cho <strong>h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/strong>\u00a0M\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh tri \u00e2n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec7m t\u1ed1t cho nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7, g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n \u0111em l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi doanh nghi\u1ec7p.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14391 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1146\" height=\"560\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14386 \" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"962\" height=\"540\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Xay_dung_ke_hoach_ho_so\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">X\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch h\u1ed3 s\u01a1<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng, \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u01a1 b\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh v\u00e0 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9, bao g\u1ed3m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, th\u1eddi gian t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c chi ti\u1ebft, ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1 cho b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Trien_khai_ke_hoach\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">Tri\u1ec3n khai k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, thi c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n <strong>h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c.<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-14387 \" src=\"https:\/\/achaumedia.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/09\/dich_vu_to_chuc_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"955\" height=\"446\" \/><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"To_chuc_chuong_trinh_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">T\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sau khi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n chu\u1ea9n ch\u1ec9nh c\u00e1c b\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean, \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd d\u1ef1 tr\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng r\u1ee7i ro kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng c\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_thuc_chuong_trinh_hoi_nghi_khach_hang_doi_tac\"><\/span><span style=\"color: #0000ff;\">K\u1ebft th\u00fac ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Ph\u1ea7n k\u1ebft th\u00fac ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb k\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p.<\/p>\n<p>Sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c thanh l\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng<\/p>\n<p><em><strong>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c h\u00e3y li\u00ean h\u1ec7 ngay v\u1edbi \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media nh\u00e9! V\u1edbi h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng trong l\u0129nh v\u1ef1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o mang t\u1edbi cho b\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam xin vui l\u00f2ng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media hotline 0943538282 ho\u1eb7c email: lienhe@sonamedia.vn ! R\u1ea5t h\u00e2n h\u1ea1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Qu\u00fd Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/strong><\/em><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>\u00c1 Ch\u00e2u media t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng ty t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam; c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c\u00a0v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u quy m\u00f4 v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1ch nhau. V\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u00ean gia c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m kinh nghi\u1ec7m, vi\u1ec7c kh\u1ea3o&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[94,65,51,767,89,88,115],"tags":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v18.7 (Yoast SEO v19.9) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>D\u1ecaCH V\u1ee4 T\u1ed4 CH\u1ee8C H\u1ed8I NGH\u1eca KH\u00c1CH H\u00c0NG, \u0110\u1ed0I T\u00c1C CHUY\u00caN NGHI\u1ec6P T\u1ea0I MI\u1ec0N B\u1eaeC - \u00c1 Ch\u00e2u Media Digital Marketing<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Chuy\u00ean t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c h\u1ed9i ngh\u1ecb, s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c chuy\u0